        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">OVERFLOW, OVERDO, OVERLOAD, OVERWORK, OVERSPEND, OVEREAT</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Spatial / Position</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">OVERHEAD, OVERLAP, OVERLOOK, OVERVIEW, OVERPASS, OVERLAY</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2">Competition</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">OVERCOME, OVERPOWER, OVERTAKE, OVERRIDE, OVERRULE, OUTVOTE</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400 mb-2">Short Forms</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">OVER, OVERT, OVERS, OVERED, OVERLY</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Short Word Pills -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-3">Quick-Play Short Words</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVER — 7 pts</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVERT — 8 pts</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVERS — 8 pts</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVARY — 11 pts</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVALS — 8 pts</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium">OVOID — 9 pts</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Strategy Tips -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-3">Strategy Tips for OVER-</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-1">V Tile Deployment</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">V is worth 4 points and notoriously tricky to place. OVER- guarantees a productive V placement every time. Hold V+E+R together on your rack and scan the board for an O already played — instant prefix foundation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-1">Extend Existing Words</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">If JOY is on the board, OVERJOYED is a massive 23-point bingo. TAX becomes OVERTAXED, KILL becomes OVERKILL — scan for short words near right-side edges where OVER- can attach in front.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 mb-1">Bingo Machine</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">OVER uses 4 tiles, so you need just 3 more from your rack for a 7-letter bingo (+50 bonus). OVER+COME, OVER+LOOK, OVER+FLOW — short roots make bingos achievable without obscure vocabulary.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cross Links -->
    <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 border border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-800 mb-8">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Related Prefix Guides</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/words-starting-with-out/" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline text-sm">Words Starting With OUT- →</a>
        <a href="/blog/words-starting-with-sub/" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline text-sm">Words Starting With SUB- →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Related Articles -->
    <aside class="mb-8 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">More Prefix Guides</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/blog/words-starting-with-inter/" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Words Starting With INTER- →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/words-starting-with-pre/" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Words Starting With PRE- →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/words-starting-with-ex/" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Words Starting With EX- →</a></li>
      </ul>
